---
title: Festive Gravy A Rich and Delicious Gravy
description: A good gravy has the power to transform a meal. Our festive gravy is just that and can be made in advance, simply reheating on the day to save you time. Its rich taste is the perfect accompaniment to your delicately flavoured turkey.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/christmas-gravy-293ea39f.jpg
